summary: An Ordinance transferring the sum of Two Hundred Twenty-five and 24/100 (225.24) Dollars from Local Improvement District No. 553 Fund, into the General Fund of the City of Seattle, for the purpose of reimbursing said General Fund, for the deficiency in the fixed estimate, for the improvement of Jackson Street, by constructing concrete sidewalks thereon, as provided for in Ordinance No.7813.
